==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: bù huān ér sàn
===[[Min Nan]]===
[[POJ]]: put-hoan-lî-sàn
===Idiom===
'''[[不]][[歡]][[而]][[散]]'''
# part [break up; end; disperse] in discord [with ill feelings; anger]; break up in disagreement; depart unhappily; end on a sour note; part in dudgeon; part on bad terms.

